# API Context Rule

Use these references when the task touches endpoints or API calls:

- `AI skills/api-endpoints.md`
- `AI skills/project-context.md`
- `AI skills/AI_STREAMING_WEBSOCKETS.md`

## Expected checks

- Keep routes under `/api/...`.
- Validate data using `Pydantic` and `SQLModel`.
- Write unit tests using `TestClient` in `backend/tests/`.
